Usage: deleteBumpConnectTargetConstraint [-help] {-bump <string> | -selected  | -all } [-instName <string> [-pinName <string> [-portNum <integer>]]]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-all                    # delete bump connect target constraint on all bumps
                        # (bool, required)
-bump <string>          # delete bump connect target constraint on specified
                        # bump (string list, required)
-instName <string>      # delete the bump connect target constraint related to
                        # inst (string, optional)
-pinName <string>       # delete the bump connect target constraint related to
                        # pin (string, optional)
-portNum <integer>      # delete the bump connect target constraint related to
                        # port number (int, optional)
-selected               # delete bump connect target constraint on selected
                        # bumps (bool, required)